public class MapViewGadgetsImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements MapViewGadgets

An implementation of the model object 'Map View Gadgets'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Layer Switcher
  • Background Map Map Service Name
  • Background Map Switcher Label
  • Background Photo Aerial Map Service Name
  • Background Photo Aerial Switcher Label
  • Point Editing Active
  • Line Editing Active
  • Polygon Editing Active
  • Modify Editing Active
